"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/52/18250?source=related_link\">",
"      Epidemiology, pathology, and pathogenesis of renal cell carcinoma",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
